metadata.description:
This vault invests into [Pendle PT Markets](https://app.pendle.finance/trade/markets) and automatically rolls them gas-free into the next maturity upon expiry.

Read the [Pendle Docs](https://docs.pendle.finance/) to learn about the associated risks.
